Editor's Note:
Our News Editor, Peter Hutchison, has
contributed a special article for this last issue, taken from his web
page at http://www.pcguru.plus.com. It is the History of the Amiga,
and you can view it inoneof two ways.
{pp}
first, there's the text-only form to be found at this link:
{link history.text}History{end}.
{pp}
Second is the full HTML version, complete with pictures, to be found
in this issue under "AIOIssue71/data/AmigaHistory/history.html"; either pop
it into your favorite browser or just click {link AmigaHistory/history.html}here{end}.
{pp}
Either way, it's a good read.  -Mark
